aptisRegModule.description: Registration subtree of Nortel Networks Aptis Enterprise MIB

aptis_modules.name: aptis_modules
aptis_modules.description: Subtree to register the values assigned to modules with the MODULE-IDENTITY construct.

aptis_systems.name: aptis_systems
aptis_systems.description: Subtree to register the values assigned to complete systems. These are registered in the MIB-II systemGroup.sysObjectID.

aptis_cards.name: aptis_cards
aptis_cards.description: Subtree to register the values assigned to slot cards inside systems. These part numbers are no longer being used.

aptis_components.name: aptis_components
aptis_components.description: Subtree to register the values assigned to managed objects for the system components inside the software. These are referenced in componenentTableEntry.componentType.
